<p>м№ґл“њмќ м†Ќм„±м¶”к°ЂлЎњ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">return</code>н• л•Њ лЄ‡к°Ђм§Ђ л‹¬лќјм§„ м ђмќґ мћ€мЉµл‹€л‹¤. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">renderFrames</code>л©”м„њл“њк°Ђ кё°мЎґм—ђ л‹Ёмќј н…њн”Њл¦їмќ„ м¶њл Ґн•лЌ л¶Ђл¶„мќґ м—¬лџ¬ к°њлЎњ л‚л‰м–ґ л ЊлЌ”лђ©л‹€л‹¤. л ЊлЌ” н›„м—ђлЉ” <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">el*</code>ліЂм€м—ђ м—л €л©нЉёк°Ђ н• л‹№лђ©л‹€л‹¤.</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardDraw</code>лЉ” <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Model</code>м—ђм„њ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">isStaged</code>к°Ђ ліЂкІЅлђњ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardStock</code>мќ„ л°›мЉµл‹€л‹¤. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">clearStock</code>мњјлЎњ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">view</code>лҐј мґ€кё°н™” м‹њн‚¤кі  <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">staged</code>л°°м—ґмќ„ м—­м€њмњјлЎњ м¶њл Ґм‹њн‚¤кі  м¶њл Ґлђњ мљ”м†Њм—ђ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">left</code> мЉ¤нѓЂмќј м†Ќм„±мќ„ м¤м„њ м№ґл“њк°Ђ кІ№м№л©ґм„њ мќґкІ©лђлЏ„лЎќ н•©л‹€л‹¤.</p>

<p>л‚м¤‘м—ђ м№ґл“њк°Ђ л‹¤ м†Њм§„лђм—€мќ„ л•ЊлҐј м¤Ђл№„н•ґм„њ лЄЁл“  м№ґл“њк°Ђ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">staged</code>лђл©ґ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">stop</code>нЃґлћмЉ¤лҐј л¶Ђм—¬н•лЏ„лЎќ н•©л‹€л‹¤. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">stop</code>нЃґлћмЉ¤к°Ђ л¶Ђм—¬лђл©ґ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">css</code>лЎњ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pointer-events</code>лҐј <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">none</code>н•к±°л‚ м•„к№Њ л§Њл“¤м—€лЌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">controller</code>мЃм—­м—ђм„њ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">stop</code>нЃґлћмЉ¤лҐј н•„н„°н•©л‹€л‹¤. мќґлЇё <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">card</code>м™Ђ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">front</code>л§Њ м„ лі„н•лЇЂлЎњ л”°лЎњ н•„н„° мћ‘м—…мќЂ мќґл ‡кІЊ л”°лќјм¤м…Ёл‹¤л©ґ м•€н•м…”лЏ„ лђ©л‹€л‹¤.</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardCollect</code>лЏ„ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Model</code>м—ђм„њ мІл¦¬лђњ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardStack</code>мќ„ л°›мЉµл‹€л‹¤. л‘к°™мќґ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">clear</code>л©”м„њл“њлЎњ мґ€кё°н™”н•кі  <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardStack</code>мќ„ м€њнљЊн•ґм„њ м»¬лџјмќ„ м–»кі  м»¬лџјмќ„ м€њнљЊн•ґм„њ м№ґл“њмќ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">suit</code>м •ліґлЎњ мЉ¤нѓќлђлЉ” м»¬лџјмќ мќёлЌ±мЉ¤лҐј м°ѕм•„ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">insert</code>н•©л‹€л‹¤.</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardPlaying</code>л©”м„њл“њлЏ„ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardCollect</code>м™Ђ л§€м°¬к°Ђм§ЂлЎњ м»¬лџјмќ„ м€њнљЊн•ґм„њ н•ґл‹№ мЃм—­мќ„ л ЊлЌ”н•кі  <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardDraw</code>м™Ђ к°™мќґ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">top</code> мЉ¤нѓЂмќјмќ„ м¦ќк°Ђм‹њмјњ мњ„м—ђм„њ м•„лћлЎњ кІ№м№лЏ„лЎќ н•©л‹€л‹¤.</p>

<p>м•ћм„њ л§ђм”Ђл“њл¦° <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cardRender</code>л©”м„њл“њлЎњ лЄЁл“  мЃм—­мќ„ н•л‚мќ л©”м„њл“њлЎњ л ЊлЌ”л§Ѓн•лЏ„лЎќ л¬¶мЉµл‹€л‹¤.</p>

